OL,5, A convicted child abuser has been found
OL,6, guilty of brutally murdering a         
OL,7, seven-year-old girl more than 30 years 
OL,8, ago.                                   
OL,10,FNikki Allan was repeatedly hit about   
OL,11,Fthe head with a brick and stabbed      
OL,12,Fdozens of times in Sunderland in       
OL,13,FOctober 1992.                          
OL,15,FProsecutors told Newcastle Crown Court 
OL,16,Fshe was then "dumped like rubbish" in a
OL,17,Fderelict building near her home.       
OL,19,FDavid Boyd, 55, from Stockton-on-Tees, 
OL,20,Fwas convicted after a three-week trial.
OL,21,FHe will be sentenced on 23 May.        
